    "name": "The Gambit Lost to Time",
    "steam_appid": 3263640,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是一位能够穿越时空的女神，在醒来时，闻到的不是清晨咖啡的香气，而是灾难的恶臭，以及一个令人不寒而栗的事实：你意识到，预示世界末日的号角已经响起。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你伪装成一位来自遥远国度的谋士，指挥军队抵抗各种各样的未知威胁。赢得战友的信任，获取关键的“洞察”，塑造更美好的未来。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>将后见之明转变为先见之明</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/d0ffd121669a82b2484f2878b8abdc2d.poster.avif?t=1772205331\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/d0ffd121669a82b2484f2878b8abdc2d.webm?t=1772205331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的优势在于策略与谋划，而非蛮力——冲锋陷阵交给由你指挥的英雄和军队就好。在四个相互交战的阵营中选择一方，带领他们的军队走向胜利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就目前而言，失败似乎不可避免。每经过一个循环，都能把后见之明变成先见之明。用你的神力制定绝妙的策略，让所有人大吃一惊。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>跨越三千条时间线的羁绊</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/aad01fa2050c584588d69c68c9f2a363.poster.avif?t=1772205331\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/aad01fa2050c584588d69c68c9f2a363.webm?t=1772205331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“这个手势只有我和艾尔莉丝知道。如果你也知道，说明我们现在就是真正的朋友！无论何时，我希望你都能把我当作朋友。拉钩起誓？”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与你的战友成为真正的朋友，互相分享内心最深处的秘密。与真正的朋友建立牢不可破的关系，就能改变未来，即使是最亵渎神明的命令，他们也愿意服从。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>执行计划的手段</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/837200373c983c9aaa92e548a81af5a0.poster.avif?t=1772205331\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/837200373c983c9aaa92e548a81af5a0.webm?t=1772205331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每一支无敌的军队，背后都有合适的基础设施，帮助他们发展壮大。将不起眼的小镇打造成繁荣美丽的堡垒，为军队提供必要的后勤。让这里成为希望的灯塔，抵御笼罩这个世界的厄运和阴郁。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>女神的调查</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/e0390df18053755ce76b1e71b527dff4.poster.avif?t=1772205331\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3263640/extras/e0390df18053755ce76b1e71b527dff4.webm?t=1772205331\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用当地的酒馆调查灾难背后的原因，或者让战败的敌人交代情报。日复一日，了解的信息就会越来越多。运用收集到的情报，暂时拖慢敌人的脚步，最终一劳永逸地击败他们。</p>",
